from:https://docs.docker.com/engine/installation/linux/docker-ce/centos/#install-from-a-package

1. 查找 安装包

2.安装
yum install  https://download.docker.com/linux/centos/7/x86_64/stable/Packages/docker-ce-17.09.0.ce-1.el7.centos.x86_64.rpm

3.开启
$ sudo systemctl start docker

4.测试一下 使用 hello-world
Verify that docker is installed correctly by running the hello-world image.

$ sudo docker run hello-world

5.卸载

$ sudo yum remove docker-ce

Images, containers, volumes, or customized configuration files on your host are not automatically removed. To delete all images, containers, and volumes:

6.删除
$ sudo rm -rf /var/lib/docker
You must delete any edited configuration files manually.
